magazine_service

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • magazine_service.Customer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AssociateCustomer, PayingCustomer

    public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Customer class represents a customer of the magazine service. It contains information about the customer's name, email, and subscribed supplements.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
